---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Me" sideBarActiveItemID="about">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">About Me</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify text-base">
    I'm <b>Jhames Andrew Macabata</b>, a Computer Science graduate from 8Con Academy in the Philippines.
    I'm building toward a career at the intersection of software engineering, data, and AI —
    domains I find genuinely exciting because they produce things that work in the real world.
    My background started on the frontend (HTML, JavaScript, web apps), and I'm now deliberately
    expanding into backend development, data engineering, and machine learning through hands-on project work.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-4">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Open to</div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-10">
    <div class="card bg-base-200 border border-base-300">
      <div class="card-body p-4">
        <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50 mb-1">Software Engineering</div>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-80 m-0">Full-stack web apps with real backends, auth, databases, and production deployment.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card bg-base-200 border border-base-300">
      <div class="card-body p-4">
        <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50 mb-1">Data Engineering</div>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-80 m-0">Automated pipelines, transformations, and dashboards that turn raw data into usable insights.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card bg-base-200 border border-base-300">
      <div class="card-body p-4">
        <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50 mb-1">AI / Machine Learning</div>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-80 m-0">End-to-end ML projects: clean data, train models, explain predictions, deploy demos.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── TECHNICAL SKILLS — Architecture graph ── -->
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Technical skills</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">

    <!-- Layer 0: Languages (foundation) -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mb-1">
      <div class="arch-box w-full max-w-sm">
        <div class="arch-label">Languages</div>
        <div class="arch-chips">
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/python" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Python</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/javascript" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>JavaScript</span>
          <span class="arch-chip arch-chip-abbr">SQL</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Arrow down -->
    <div class="flex justify-center my-1">
      <svg width="2" height="20" viewBox="0 0 2 20" class="opacity-30"><line x1="1" y1="0" x2="1" y2="16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="1,20 -2,14 4,14" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.5"/></svg>
    </div>

    <!-- Layer 1: Backend + Frontend -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-1">
      <div class="arch-box">
        <div class="arch-label">Backend</div>
        <div class="arch-chips">
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/fastapi" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>FastAPI</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/nodedotjs" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Node.js</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/express" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Express</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/strapi" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Strapi</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="arch-box">
        <div class="arch-label">Frontend</div>
        <div class="arch-chips">
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/react" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>React</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/htmx" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>HTMX</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/tailwindcss" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Tailwind</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Arrow down -->
    <div class="flex justify-center my-1">
      <svg width="2" height="20" viewBox="0 0 2 20" class="opacity-30"><line x1="1" y1="0" x2="1" y2="16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="1,20 -2,14 4,14" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.5"/></svg>
    </div>

    <!-- Layer 2: Databases + Data & ML -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-1">
      <div class="arch-box">
        <div class="arch-label">Databases</div>
        <div class="arch-chips">
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/postgresql" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>PostgreSQL</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/mysql" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>MySQL</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/duckdb" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>DuckDB</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/redis" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Redis</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/supabase" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Supabase</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="arch-box">
        <div class="arch-label">Data &amp; ML</div>
        <div class="arch-chips">
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/pandas" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>pandas</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/dbt" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>dbt</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/scikitlearn" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>scikit-learn</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/streamlit" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Streamlit</span>
          <span class="arch-chip arch-chip-abbr">XGBoost</span>
          <span class="arch-chip arch-chip-abbr">SHAP</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Arrow down -->
    <div class="flex justify-center my-1">
      <svg width="2" height="20" viewBox="0 0 2 20" class="opacity-30"><line x1="1" y1="0" x2="1" y2="16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="1,20 -2,14 4,14" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.5"/></svg>
    </div>

    <!-- Layer 3: DevOps & Infra -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mb-1">
      <div class="arch-box w-full">
        <div class="arch-label">DevOps &amp; Infra</div>
        <div class="arch-chips">
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/docker" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Docker</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/githubactions" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>GH Actions</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/nginx" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Nginx</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/git" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Git</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Arrow down -->
    <div class="flex justify-center my-1">
      <svg width="2" height="20" viewBox="0 0 2 20" class="opacity-30"><line x1="1" y1="0" x2="1" y2="16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/><polygon points="1,20 -2,14 4,14" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.5"/></svg>
    </div>

    <!-- Layer 4: Platforms & Tools -->
    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <div class="arch-box w-full">
        <div class="arch-label">Platforms &amp; Tools</div>
        <div class="arch-chips">
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/render" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Render</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/railway" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Railway</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/huggingface" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Hugging Face</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/visualstudiocode" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>VS Code</span>
          <span class="arch-chip"><img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/jupyter" class="w-3 h-3" alt=""/>Jupyter</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
  <!-- ── end architecture graph ── -->

  <div class="mb-4">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">How I work</div>
  </div>

  <div class="card bg-base-200 border-l-4 border-neutral rounded-l-none mb-10">
    <div class="card-body p-5 text-base text-justify">
      I learn best by building real things with a clear purpose. Each project in this portfolio solves an actual problem,
      ships to a live URL, and reflects what I'd bring to a real team — not just "I followed a tutorial." I'm comfortable
      asking for help when stuck, breaking problems into small steps, and iterating toward something that actually works.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-4">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Goals</div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-10">
    <div class="card bg-base-200 border border-base-300">
      <div class="card-body p-4">
        <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50 mb-2">Short-term</div>
        <p class="text-sm m-0">Land an entry-level role where I can contribute quickly and grow fast.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card bg-base-200 border border-base-300">
      <div class="card-body p-4">
        <div class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-50 mb-2">Long-term</div>
        <p class="text-sm m-0">Become a well-rounded engineer who can move fluidly between software, data, and ML layers — someone who understands a business problem end-to-end and can build a solution for it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-4">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="card bg-base-200 border border-base-300 mb-10">
    <div class="card-body p-4">
      <div class="font-bold">Bachelor of Science in Computer Science</div>
      <div class="text-sm opacity-60">8Con Academy &nbsp;·&nbsp; Philippines</div>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .arch-box {
    @apply bg-base-200 border border-base-300 rounded-xl p-3;
  }
  .arch-label {
    @apply text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-2;
  }
  .arch-chips {
    @apply flex flex-wrap gap-1.5;
  }
  .arch-chip {
    @apply inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-base-100 border border-base-300 text-[11px] font-medium;
  }
  .arch-chip-abbr {
    @apply font-semibold opacity-70;
  }
</style>
